HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Displays the help menu
Displays your current balance
Redeems the daily credit gift (24 hours)
Displays your debt, better pay it off!
Borrows money from the bank, but remember, it's a loan!
Returns borrowed money to the bank
Transfers money to the mentioned user
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [@user] | A @mention of the user you want to transfer money to [amount] | The amount of money you want to transfer to the mentioned user

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: It's all over now...
Engage in the act of wasting your life earnings away in gambling
Displays stocks currently owned by you
Displays the stock market along with current stock prices
Buys selected stock at stock market price
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [stockTicker] | The symbol of the stock, such as EA, AAPL [amount] | Amount of specified stock to buy

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Sells selected stock at stock market price
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [stockTicker] | The symbol of the stock, such as EA, AAPL [amount] | Amount of specified stock to sell

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Opens a CS:GO case, maybe you will get a knife?
Get an item drop, lesser in quality compared to a case open
Opens the case selection menu
Displays your current inventory of CS:GO skins
Displays current market of CS:GO skins along with their prices
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [Optional: filterText] | Optional, Only show items containing filter text

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Buys specified item from CS:GO skin market
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsage: .d cs buy [skinName] // .d cs buy P250 | Sand Dune (Well-Worn)
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [skinName] | Name of skin you want to buy

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Sells selected CS:GO skins from your inventory, to sell all skins, use `*` for skin name
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsage: .d cs sell [skinName] //.d cs sell AUG | Aristocrat (Field-Tested)
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [skinName] | Name of skin to sell, **use `*` to sell all skins**

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Sells ALL selected CS:GO skins from your inventory
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [skinName] | Words item must contain to be sold

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Displays information about the selected item
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsage: .d cs info [skinName] //.d cs info AUG | Aristocrat (Field-Tested)
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [skinName] | Name of skin to get information on

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Lists the available roles you can assign yourself
Adds the specified role to yourself
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [roleName] | Name of role from .d role list

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Removes the specified role to yourself
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [roleName] | Name of role from .d role list

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Deletes specified number of messages from current channel
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [deleteAmount] | Amount of messages to delete [@deleteAuthor] | @mention of user to delete specified number of messages from

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Adds the specified role to guild list
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [@roleMention] | A @mention of the role [roleName] | Name of role from .d role list

HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandDescription: Removes the specified role from guild list
HelpMenuCommandEntry.CommandUsageDefinition: [@roleMention] | A @mention of the role [roleName] | Name of role from .d role list
